    <stitle>Spanish - Gu&#237;a para Localizaci&#243;n de Fallas del Sistema El&#233;ctrico - 3200, 4200, 4300, 4400,
        7300, 7400, 7500, 8500, 8600 - FRONT AXLE LOCKING HUBS - REMOVE
    </stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="remove" graphiccount="0">
        <title>REMOVE</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the six Allen head capscrews that secure the clutch assembly to the hub body.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the clutch assembly and gasket from the hub body.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the bolt that secures the axle stop plug.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the eight 7/16-20 locknuts that secure the hub body onto the wheel end and pull the
                body and gasket clear.
            </para>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
